    "name": "Check & Clean",
    "steam_appid": 2368840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/a3bbb95401a7eb829c66737d318d6ae5.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=600 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/a3bbb95401a7eb829c66737d318d6ae5.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Check&amp;Clean is a tactical First Person Shooter blending music, speedrun elements and intense action. It immerses you in a rhythmic universe, alternating analysis sequences and gunfights. The innovative music coordination allows players to synchronize explosive moments with beats. </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have multiple tools to escape your robbery nightmare: <strong>Weapons, C4, cameras, ammunition boxes and mines</strong>. Take care of analyzing different rooms before entering in. Informations are crucial in our game. You will not survive if you enter a room without analyzing environment first. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>« Every night, I have the same nightmare. I’m pulling a heist. Stuck in a room, there is only one exit : a locked door. It can be a hotel, an office, a basement, or a laboratory. But everytime, it begins the same way… I choose a weapon. »</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MUSIC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The innovative music coordination allows players to synchronize explosive moments with beats.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/01c5f17380263f7305c16f7010e897b7.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/01c5f17380263f7305c16f7010e897b7.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/01c5f17380263f7305c16f7010e897b7.mp4?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are several weapons you can unlock by completing levels. Each weapon can be customized and adapted to your style with unlockable In-Game attachments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/f808007fc7b39fbe453b00d410474161.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/f808007fc7b39fbe453b00d410474161.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/f808007fc7b39fbe453b00d410474161.mp4?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CAMERAS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each level, there are 5 cameras giving you perspective to 5 different rooms. Cameras allow you to anticipate enemies position, ammo boxes position, and mines position. <strong>CHECK !</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/e87b01e22de21b589ba277f723faeb18.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/e87b01e22de21b589ba277f723faeb18.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/e87b01e22de21b589ba277f723faeb18.mp4?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >C4</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use C4 to destroy doors and clean areas. Pay attention to know all the details hidden behind the door before destroying it. <strong>CLEAN !</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/d51d12065b2e9f9e928379d4bb810010.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/d51d12065b2e9f9e928379d4bb810010.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/d51d12065b2e9f9e928379d4bb810010.mp4?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AMMUNITION BOX</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different ammunition boxes are concealed in the rooms. You won’t survive without finding them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/ba42053b2152c19ebb7ceb16437a9624.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/ba42053b2152c19ebb7ceb16437a9624.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/ba42053b2152c19ebb7ceb16437a9624.mp4?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MINES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several mines are hidden in the rooms. Be extremely vigilant, and use them to your advantage. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/83cc657f8bf29ea881c51016da318463.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/83cc657f8bf29ea881c51016da318463.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/83cc657f8bf29ea881c51016da318463.mp4?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RANDOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check&amp;Clean also claims to be a memory game. There are several randomization systems to force the player to analyze their environment and optimize the replayability experience. Randomization affects enemy positions, ammunition boxes position, and mines position. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/ab24be189810142c16d3400c536f9ffa.poster.avif?t=1742806985\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/ab24be189810142c16d3400c536f9ffa.webm?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/ab24be189810142c16d3400c536f9ffa.mp4?t=1742806985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
